ğŸ’° Gifting + Pricing Design

Tiered Pricing:

Tier	Spend Range	Unlocks

I	$0â€“$9 / 0â€“0.0001 BTC	1 free cosmetic (skin, voice)
II	$10â€“$49 / ~0.0002 BTC	1 item + 1 stat buff
